            <div class="welovestackoverflow" style="margin-top: 10px;">
                <div style="float: left;">
                        <p>
Patch Management refers to updating and patching systems, and particularly to tools and systems which automate this process for a large number of systems.                         </p>
                                            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
                            <a title="tag wiki" href="/tags/patch-management/info">learn more&hellip;</a>
